## **Become a Certified NRA Instructor**

Are you ready to take the next step in your firearms journey? The NRA Instructor Pistol Shooting Course is the premier certification for those looking to teach the basics of pistol safety and marksmanship. As an NRA Instructor, you'll be part of a nationwide network of professionals dedicated to promoting safe and responsible gun ownership.

### **Prerequisites**

- Must be a legal resident of the United States.
- Must demonstrate advanced pistol shooting skills.
- Must have completed the NRA Basic Pistol Shooting Course.
- Must pass the pre-course qualification and assessment.

If you have any questions, call [1-571-210-5651](tel:15712105651), or email at [class@livefireinstruction.com](mailto:class@livefireinstruction.com)
